summary: I’m back with my once a month art^^  So this is Habit. He’s actually a demon canine that’s close to the size of Cerberus, buuuut...
caption:
I’m back with my once a month art^^

So this is Habit. He’s actually a demon canine that’s close to the size of Cerberus, buuuut I can’t draw animals to save my life so I gave him a temporary human form. I also couldn’t decide if I liked the picture with or without the glowing eye so I just upload both.
He’s connected to another character of mines named Sage (because Sage got a huge rework after I made them, but that’s another story >>)
The tattoo takes up most of his back, it’s in white ink and glows…but that’s also another story ^^;;
And the sigil on his skull is actually his name. I used a guide to make it.

I’m also getting better with writing my signature on my tablet. So there’s that lol
